{"tid":1930094,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"李桂華稱自己非常驚","createTime":"2020-03-17T10:30:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-17T10:55:51.000Z","uid":326897,"like":7,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"9e7751a102241f3acb35de8ff382387dfb21c025","tid":1930094,"uid":326897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T10:30:07.000Z","msg":"李桂華稱自己曾遇示威者路障感到非常驚<br />\n2020-03-17 HKT 17:11<br />\n <a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1515047-20200317.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1515047-20200317.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Ih%2BYJd3WmO0qFhbj2imzB13VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=aa05390f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1515047-20200317.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=2e565bde\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1515047-20200317.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n監警會與投訴警察課代表舉行例會，由警方報告「大型公眾活動中暴力升級的情況」。<br />\n<br />\n有組織罪案及三合會調查科高級警司李桂華說，由觸發反修例示威至今拘捕7500多人，其中約37%被捕人年齡介乎11至20歲，學生佔總被捕人數約4成，又指16歲以下及中學生的被捕人數比例，有上升趨勢。<br />\n<br />\n他在會上歸納示威者在事件中所用的不同手法，包括散播假消息、起底、用「私了」等方法排除異己、以路障等癱瘓社會、及使用汽油彈、爆炸品等不同武器。<br />\n<br />\n李桂華表示，整個反修例事件越來越暴力，提到有人散播8.31太子站有人死亡的假消息，但永遠沒有人報警；散播新屋嶺有性罪行的假消息，但就以不應再傷害受害人作掩飾，沒有提供事件詳情。他認為假消息會成為仇恨的種子，難以證實沒有發生過的事情。<br />\n<br />\n另外，他提到有示威者將警員「起底」，又曾設置路障查問每一輛車，他自己曾經過相關路障，在被查問前立刻駛走，指自己當時非常驚，認為相關行為對警員的心理打擊很大。<br />\n<br />\n李桂華說，部分被捕年輕人有禮貌及聰明，認為只有一個原因，是憤恨、嬲怒，令他們脫離人性。<br />\n<br />\n由於新型冠狀病毒疫情，監警會透過網上直播今次會議，不設公眾席和傳媒席。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">驚就唔好出街嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 出嚟又要驚, 驚都啱嘅, <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好快3萬隻武炎警甴就做condom 俾清算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"38d696720f372e1adfdb164f45961a5acc91bf44","tid":1930094,"uid":20170,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T10:32:09.000Z","msg":"驚就唔好出街"},{"pid":"1757334418c3c5a4e3adde70137cb328c7a4a5cf","tid":1930094,"uid":115212,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T10:32:17.000Z","msg":"我哋都未話驚你哋班香港恐怖分子<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你驚乜春呀李桂華"},{"pid":"b28fde04ca111dcd10a5a994fbcee38ee5d53ce6","tid":1930094,"uid":25105,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T10:33:05.000Z","msg":"唔去現場咪唔驚"},{"pid":"387181527e128898c154f03b7387504eda615da1","tid":1930094,"uid":36901,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T10:34:29.000Z","msg":"831行得正企得正,做乜唔交cctv?<br />\n新屋嶺行得正企得正做乜又關左佢?"},{"pid":"f55f21ee8c965a907d0c180c2719abc9ffa361e0","tid":1930094,"uid":1049,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T10:34:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pKdtnPX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpKdtnPX.png&h=c618ca4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n條友應該係驚自己俾人認撚到姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d84d70796cc551397eda7381843496f4a893e69","tid":1930094,"uid":81052,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T10:34:43.000Z","msg":"駛走，而唔係拉人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af570878e08d567b981930edb4bc4b2f5e953d9a","tid":1930094,"uid":280056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T10:36:21.000Z","msg":"瀆職<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f5dfbe94ff41b0dafb1abb0c36a8e6afe2f8cd5","tid":1930094,"uid":85396,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T10:37:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.whatscap.com/edc/af7/edcaf7de09e14e1ce146d74ade35171af2f49f54_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.whatscap.com%2Fedc%2Faf7%2Fedcaf7de09e14e1ce146d74ade35171af2f49f54_b.jpg&h=fe151d3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢都未撚驚<br />\n讓個位俾佢啦，反正識奶共識吠就做得"},{"pid":"6bc2cc33d10087a891d34e533515cb23d8d4f1ed","tid":1930094,"uid":34789,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T10:37:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/78526175_2557098710994116_5137628463452127232_o_LihV0_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F78526175_2557098710994116_5137628463452127232_o_LihV0_1200x0.png&h=6a00117a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n邊個多人驚D呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9257d7e836f83e5318c00418e65fd26ce0e55f1","tid":1930094,"uid":271894,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T10:37:56.000Z","msg":"咁你監狗會要黎托柒 <br />\n監條閪？同個做operation 一齊見記者同佢揸住枝槍叫你講班狗無犯法有咩分別"},{"pid":"8816bc1f66e86cca262c0ba7b78e3131e43099cf","tid":1930094,"uid":318069,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T10:38:29.000Z","msg":"重點係佢<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">老屈路障=查車！</span></span>"},{"pid":"196a9d939ea5cf3fae5ab24a5374c5c5bbd9cd90","tid":1930094,"uid":28970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T10:38:58.000Z","msg":"好人好者驚閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51d54c11ace809787d82d43c6f59420d612975c8","tid":1930094,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T10:39:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"90a020a75a06869e87b1eb8434a77a264d77a7d9","tid":1930094,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T10:40:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已