7T10:38:29.000Z","msg":"重點係佢<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">老屈路障=查車！</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T10:43:15.000Z","msg":"再配合埋邱文勁呢篇文<br />\n<br />\n反恐條例魔鬼細節&mdash;<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">堵路成為恐怖主義行為</span></span>？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1929924\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1929924</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n要做好文宣，唔好傻更更跟佢講驚驚就算！"},{"pid":"d78f93c294227eaed817bee28696311102209f71","tid":1930094,"uid":14422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63b30fb76379bc4d28afecddc70c04922f4b9f32","tid":1930094,"uid":204539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d84d70796cc551397eda7381843496f4a893e69","tid":1930094,"uid":81052,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T10:34:43.000Z","msg":"駛走，而唔係拉人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T10:41:25.000Z","msg":"同721一撚樣呀<br />\n亞洲最優秀呀！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T10:45:45.000Z","msg":"駛走？又話忠誠勇毅？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4b4556d41d5932bcc151cfe2fec4139b5e2e7e4","tid":1930094,"uid":78392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T10:48:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">監警會監察市民？      </span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6344030bb34e2cf572ffb8827b26c829143b7da1","tid":1930094,"uid":335434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d84d70796cc551397eda7381843496f4a893e69","tid":1930094,"uid":81052,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T10:34:43.000Z","msg":"駛走，而唔係拉人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T10:55:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>另外，他提到有示威者將警員「起底」，又曾設置路障查問每一輛車，他自己曾經過相關路障，在被查問前立刻駛走，指自己當時非常驚，認為相關行為對警員的心理打擊很大。</blockquote><br />\n根據香港法例第232A章《警察(紀律)規例》<br />\n<blockquote>3.違紀行為<br />\n(1)任何督察或初級警務人員，如犯第(2)款所指明的違紀行為，並 &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n(a)在適當審裁體席前認罪；或<br />\n(b)經適當審裁體裁斷犯罪，<br />\n則可由該審裁體按照本規例予以懲罰。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>(2)違紀行為指</strong></span></span> &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n(a)沒有許可或妥善因由而擅離職守；<br />\n(b)當值時睡覺；<br />\n(c)對良好秩序及紀律有損的行為；<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">(d)執行職責時怯懦</span></strong></span>；<br />\n(e)違反警察規例或任何書面或口頭的警察命令；<br />\n(f)不服從上級；<br />\n(g)由於昏醉而不適宜執行職責；<br />\n(h)疏於職守或忽視命令；<br />\n(i)裝病；<br />\n(j)在執行職責的過程中，或在關乎警隊履行任何職責或職能方面，作出在要項上屬虛假的陳述；<br />\n(k)不合法或不必要地行使權能，引致其他人或政府蒙受損失或損害；<br />\n(l)蓄意破壞政府財產或因疏忽致令政府財產遺失或損壞；<br />\n(m)其行為刻意致使公共服務聲譽受損。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n李桂華高級警司喺遇到由市民設立嘅「路障」掉頭走 <br />\n究竟係有關「路障」屬合法 定係當時出於「怯懦」而未有執行職責繼而違反咗《警察(紀律)規例》呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}